{"tid":53810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係恭喜你呀  李嘉欣全家睡機場餓凍3天","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T04:43:44.000Z","uid":48905,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0181965ec0efa3684b9badad1673bd60758aa7b1","tid":53810,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"日本北海道連日暴雪，造成新千歳機場284班航班取消，約6000名旅客在機場留宿，人數創歷史新高，機場至今仍舊混亂。JR北海道及渡輪服務相繼停駛或取消，交通網絡全日混亂。香港女星李嘉欣也是受害者，她和富商老公許晉亨舉家到北海道玩雪，因此受困機場，今凌晨12點她接受《港蘋》電訪表示和不少旅客一樣，從22日等飛機等到今天仍然回不了家！<br />\n <br />\n李嘉欣無奈地說：「沒有人想碰到50年一遇的大風雪。」並對航空公司的安排表達不滿，「我們一行7人從22號開始到今天，他們每天都說有得上機，叫大家去check in，每個都入關了，但最後又說不能飛，又得退回去。」<br />\n <br />\n李嘉欣還生氣表示「昨天等了10幾個鐘頭。沒水沒食物，完全沒人理我們，沒有工作人員來幫我們安排，真的好混亂」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/25/121925_3ea627e3f444cc0d44cb0a61d47a622b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F121925_3ea627e3f444cc0d44cb0a61d47a622b.jpg&h=84b466a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係恭喜你呀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448509b0d9055907505364187342f95e026657fb","tid":53810,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0533444373dab2a54ed8352c24e02ceb664586e","tid":53810,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"唔滯留你去機場把撚呀"},{"pid":"ed35f2f7755ca81a6a6d414ed00a186aeb3f4ae9","tid":53810,"uid":4269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔滯留你去機場把撚呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28778f5c7e87bcf2cc122eeadbc6c1a68604511","tid":53810,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2